# a [[river]]

====Declension====
{{sv-noun-reg-ar}}

====Usage notes====
* Rivers in Scandinavia north of [[Göta älv]] and [[Dalälven]] are named ''älv'', south thereof ''[[å]]'' or ''[[ström]]''. Rivers abroad are called ''[[flod]]''. Smaller streams can be called ''[[å]], [[ström]], [[bäck]]''.

